Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_uart::_srts

The shadow request to send register is a shadow register for the MIO_UART(0..1)_MCR[RTS] bit that can be used to remove the burden of having to perform a read- modify-write on MIO_UART(0..1)_MCR.
